title: Purchase of 2 Floor CryptoPunks
body: This proposal is made by Christopher Ballin and has met the quorum required for this to be a snapshot proposal. Reasoning behind this is to stay on top of other DAO's which have a higher number of CryptoPunks, in order to stay ahead of any competition.
